# Blast Radius — {{agent_id}}

> Per-agent risk envelope + autonomy posture. Build session enforces
> via cooperative agent prose AND deterministic hook
> (`hooks/autonomy-gate.sh` if using bash impl).

## Assignment

| Property | Value |
|---|---|
| Blast radius | **L{{blast_radius}}** |
| Autonomy | **{{autonomy}}**  (full / semi / supervised) |

## What L{{blast_radius}} means

{{IF blast == 1}}
**L1 — read-only.** Reads state files; reads external APIs. No writes,
no external sends. No approval gate.
{{ELIF blast == 2}}
**L2 — write-scoped.** Writes only to designated paths
(`.agentbloc/agents/{{agent_id}}/` for own state,
`.agentbloc/agents/<recipient>/inbox/` for inter-agent handoff). No
external sends. No approval gate.
{{ELIF blast == 3}}
**L3 — write-unrestricted.** Writes to arbitrary paths or runs
unrestricted Bash. Approval gate required for `semi` and `supervised`
autonomy.
{{ELIF blast == 4}}
**L4 — send-external.** Sends Telegram messages, emails, API calls
to third parties. Approval gate required for `semi` and `supervised`
autonomy. Highest risk; concentrate in 1-2 agents per team.
{{END}}

